  "texts": [
    "CodeLlama and WizardCoder are code generation LLMs, fine-tuned on Llama2 [25] and StarCoder [26], respectively.",
    "Llama-3 is the newest open-source general LLM.",
    "WizardCoder and Llama-3 are LLMs that outperformed GPT-3.5 on the HumanEval [27] coding tasks [28].",
    "We adopt the 'Pass@k' metric [29] (k=1, 5) as our main evaluation standard, a widely used approach in code generation tasks [21], [22].",
    "This metric quantifies the proportion of correct generations within k independent attempts, where higher values denote better performance."
  ],
